querysource.name: dati_ordine
querysource.sql: select ro.ordprog as "op", op.ordkey as "ok", op.opcdisl as "is", op.opcdsto as "so", ro.rodscli as "rs", ro.roincli as "in", ro.rocpcli as "ca", ro.rolocli as "lo", ro.roprcli as "pr", op.opnmcll as "cl", op.opnmrgh as "rg", op.opnmcpe as "cp", data_ora('now') as "data_ora" from ric_ord ro, ord_prod op where ro.ordprog = op.ordprog and op.ordkey= <? value(ordkey) ?> ;

querysource.name: lista_articoli_ordine
querysource.sql: select r.rpcdpro as "cd", a.prdescr as "tt", r.rpqtspe as "qt", u.settore as "st", a.prpesgr as "pg", a.prflgpp as "pp", r.rpnmcol as "nc", case when a.prqtkar>0 then a.prqtkar::text else ' ' end as "kk" from rig_prod as r, articoli as a,ubicazioni as u where u.ubicazione=r.rpcdubi and a.prcdpro=r.rpcdpro and r.ordkey = <? value(ordkey) ?> order by r.rpnmcol,u.priorita,r.rpprogr ;
